# Aliangé

> Aliangé is an Australian clinical skincare brand developed by Dr. Alison Jamieson, bringing over 40 years of dermatological expertise to evidence-based formulations. Specialising in cellular regeneration, anti-ageing, pigmentation correction, and barrier repair, every product is doctor-led, Australian made, and designed for the demands of the Queensland sun. Shop at {{ store_url }}.

